          <title>BC's Stiga scores on OT breakaway to give US 2nd straight world junior title, 4-3 over Finland</title>
          <description><![CDATA[OTTAWA, Ontario (AP) — Teddy Stiga scored on a breakaway at 8:04 of 3-on-3 overtime to give the United States a 4-3 victory over Finland on Sunday night in the world junior hockey championship game.]]></description>
