        <item>
          <title>Lions beat Vikings 31-9, win NFC North and No. 1 seed, dropping division rivals to No. 5</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Jahmyr Gibbs scored three of his franchise-record tying four touchdowns in the second half, and the Detroit Lions beat the Minnesota Vikings 31-9 to win their second straight NFC North title and earn home-field advantage until the Super Bowl.]]></description>
